Class EntityPlaceholderTypeClass

java.lang.Object
is.yarr.qilletni.api.lang.types.typeclass.QilletniTypeClass<EntityType>
is.yarr.qilletni.api.lang.types.typeclass.EntityPlaceholderTypeClass
public class EntityPlaceholderTypeClass extends QilletniTypeClass<EntityType>
A placeholder QilletniTypeClass for entities that need a type class but are not initialized yet. This is used primarily as the subtype for lists of entities if an entity has not been put in yet.
